00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:18,500
James Scott in his 1998 book, *The State Perspective: Why Projects Seeking to Improve the Human Condition Fail*. Scott's work can be seen as an autopsy report on the social engineering disasters of the 20th century. He studied a series of

112
