scientific forestry in Germany. At the end of the 18th century, Prussian forestry officials faced the problem of how to increase timber production. What were traditional German forests like?

129
00:12:01,333 --> 00:12:04,300
A mixture of various trees: oak, beech, maple, spruce, varying in height and age. The understory

