as orderly as an army formation. Forestry

134
00:12:33,433 --> 00:12:34,933
officials could now accurately

135
00:12:34,933 --> 00:12:37,533
calculate how many trees were per hectare and how many cubic meters of timber could be harvested in 10 years. The first generation was a huge success; timber production increased dramatically, and

136
