142
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:34,066
without dead branches and leaves… Nutrient cycling is disrupted. The first generation relies on the reserves accumulated by the original forest. The second generation depletes these reserves, leading to system collapse. This is the readability trap. To make forests easier to manage and calculate, you simplify their complexity. But it is precisely this complexity that maintains the health of the forest. Let's look at a

143
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:37,900
larger-scale case: the Soviet collective farms. In 1929, Stalin launched a comprehensive collectivization movement. The logic was simple: small-scale farming was inefficient, fragmented, and wasteful of resources. If land were centralized, mechanized

144
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:40,000
farming, and scientific management, yields would

145
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:45,866
certainly increase significantly.

146
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:59,233
Experts in Moscow developed detailed plans. Each collective farm had standards for what to plant, how much fertilizer to use, and when to sow and harvest. However, there was a problem: these standards were based on averages. In reality, every piece of land

147
00:14:01,833 --> 00:14:03,466
is unique. What do

148
00:14:11,633 --> 00:14:13,433
farmers in a Ukrainian village know? They know that the land north of the village has poor drainage and is prone to waterlogging in spring, making it unsuitable for

149
00:14:14,533 --> 00:14:16,733
wheat. They know that the soil on the eastern slope is poor but suitable for buckwheat.

150
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,733
They know that this year's rainfall is heavy, requiring a few days' delay in

151
00:14:29,333 --> 00:14:30,233
sowing, otherwise the seeds will rot in the ground. This knowledge is what Hayek called local knowledge, and Scott called Metis, or practical

152
00:14:48,166 --> 00:14:49,866
wisdom. However, after collectivization, this knowledge was neglected. Moscow's directive was to plant wheat, so wheat was planted regardless of the land's suitability. The directive was to sow on March 15th, so March

